<P>
Photo, Ricardo Hunter Garcia of New York checks schedule at comedy convention. 
; Photo, Earl Burks brought his dog Winston to a seminar on "Casting at Network 
Level." ; Photo, COLOR, (Cover) Clockwise from left, Tim Wilson, Lahai 
Fahnbulleh and Peter Pitovsky doing their stand-up routines at the Aemrican 
Comedy Convention. Photos by ADRIENNE HELITZER / L.A. Times; Photo, NBC casting 
director Shana Landsburg: "I don't believe in actors having to showcase." 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
