<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE BARGAIN CORNER: HOTEL CHAINS CUT RATES, OFFER SUMMER SPECIALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JACK ADLER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ramada and Hilton are making a splash with special summer programs. 
</P>
<P>
Ramada's "Summer Sale" rates start at $37 a night until Sept. 30. Up to four 
guests can share a room at no extra cost, and the offer is good throughout the 
week. Nearly 450 Ramada properties and Renaissance hotels in the United States, 
Canada and the Caribbean are participating. 
</P>
<P>
At check-in, guests receive a Budget Rent-a-Car coupon good for either $20 off 
a weekly rental or $10 off a weekend rental of two days or more on a compact or 
larger car. The car, however, must be returned to the original rental point. 
</P>
<P>
There are more than 60 hotels with summer rates under $40, all in the United 
States. Rates start at $70 for the hotels in Canada and $65 in the Caribbean. 
</P>
<P>
Hilton has extended its "BounceBack Weekend" to cover weekdays during the 
summer if stays include a Saturday night. The original program covered only 
Friday, Saturday and Sunday nights. 
</P>
<P>
Rates start at $45 per room a night. The number of guests who can stay in the 
room varies from hotel to hotel, but at least two can stay for the same price, 
according to a Hilton spokesman. 
</P>
<P>
Children of any age can stay free with one parent or grandparent. A continental 
breakfast for each guest is included. 
</P>
<P>
Rates of $65 or under are available at 176 of the more than 250 properties 
participating in the BounceBack promotion, with rates 40% to 50% off regular 
prices. 
</P>
<P>
The program is available until Sept. 4, but excluding weekdays, the program 
will continue after Sept. 4. 
</P>
<P>
Contact travel agents or Ramada toll-free at (800) 228-2828, and Hilton at 
(800) HILTONS. 
</P>
<P>
If you prefer a bed and breakfast inn, the Bed &amp; Breakfast Innkeepers of 
Southern California are offering a "Mid-Weekenders Discount Coupon Book" for 
$10. The booklet contains 24 coupons for Sunday-Thursday stays, good until the 
end of 1990 at more than 20 member inns. 
</P>
<P>
Some of the coupons set a specific dollar discount and others offer a 
percentage off room rates. Most of the dollar discounts are $10 to $30, with 
percentage discounts 10% to 25%. 
</P>
<P>
Copies can be ordered through Brookside Farm Bed &amp; Breakfast Inn, 1373 
Marron Valley Road, Dulzura, Calif. 92017. For more information, call (619) 
234-2926. JACK ADLER 
</P>
