<HEADLINE>
<P>
GUIDE LISTS TREES IN PACIFIC PALISADES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Walkers or bicyclists wanting to know more about the trees they see in Pacific 
Palisades, a guide, "Trees of Pacific Palisades," by Grace L. Heintz is 
available. A list of street trees is accompanied by a map. 
</P>
<P>
A section of the book describes growth rates of trees, mature size and watering 
needs. the 272-page book can be ordered for $5 from Palisades Beautiful, Box 
1072, Pacific Palisades, Calif. 90272. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<CORRECTION-DATE>
<P>
July 23, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</CORRECTION-DATE>
<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
The price of the 272-page guide entitled "Trees of Pacific Palisades" by Grace 
L. Heintz is $7. It can be ordered from Palisades Beautiful, Box 1072, Pacific 
Palisades, Calif. 90272. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
