Bruce L. Megowan has been named vice president of asset management at the 
Yarmouth Group Inc. He will be in charge of the company's real estate asset 
activities for its clients' properties in Southern California. The Los 
Angeles-based firm invests in commercial real estate in the United States on 
behalf of domestic and foreign pension funds and other institutional investors. 
</P>
