Peter Nielsen has joined the National Bank of Canada's Orange County real 
estate group as assistant treasurer. Nielsen will be working out of the Irvine 
office where he will be responsible for arranging construction loans for 
developers based in Orange County. LINDA MARTINI-POSNER 
