<DOCID> 79994 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 9, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Long Beach; Part 9; Page 2; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
