MISMANAGEMENT; PIERCE, SAMUEL R; KEMP, JACK; CHARITIES; CONTRIBUTIONS; DEAN, 
DEBORAH GORE; DEMERY, THOMAS T; CUSHING, R HUNTER; FOOD FOR AFRICA 
(ORGANIZATION); UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS 
</P>
