match with Boris Becker (left), who hits the ball into the Wimbledon crowd 
after winning. ; Photo, Boris Becker grimmaces as he reaches to return a shot 
to Ivan Lendl during their Wimbledon semifinal match Saturday. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
