</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BASKETBALL PLAYERS; JORDAN, MICHAEL; TRAFFIC VIOLATIONS; SPEED LIMITS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070989-0185 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 80131 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 9, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
